# 🛡️ Privacy Nudge

**Catch your data in motion.**

Privacy Nudge is an Android application that helps users understand when their apps are communicating with privacy-sensitive domains. It uses a local VPN service to monitor DNS queries and provides real-time notifications when potentially concerning network activity is detected.

