## ✨ Features

### 🔍 App Monitoring
- Select any installed app to monitor its network activity
- View app permissions including location access status
- Non-intrusive monitoring that runs in the background

### 🌐 DNS Query Detection
- Intercepts and analyzes DNS queries from monitored apps
- Detects connections to sensitive domains including:
  - **Location Services** - Google Maps, Mapbox, IP geolocation APIs
  - **Analytics & Tracking** - Google Analytics, Firebase, Mixpanel, Amplitude
  - **Advertising** - DoubleClick, AdMob, Facebook tracking
  - **Authentication** - OAuth, social login services

### 🔔 Real-time Privacy Nudges
- Push notifications when sensitive domains are contacted
- Contextual alerts showing which app accessed which service
- Permission-aware nudges (e.g., alerts when location-enabled apps contact tracking services)

### 📊 Event Logging
- In-app event log showing all detected privacy-relevant activity
- Timestamped records for review
- Clear explanations of why each event is flagged

---

## 🔧 How It Works

1. **VPN Tunnel Creation** - Creates a local VPN interface that routes traffic from the selected app
2. **Packet Interception** - Reads IP packets and extracts DNS query payloads
3. **Domain Analysis** - Parses DNS queries to extract requested domain names
4. **Pattern Matching** - Compares domains against a database of sensitive services
5. **Permission Check** - Verifies if the app has location permissions (heightened concern)
6. **User Notification** - Sends push notification and logs the event in-app

---

## 🏗️ Architecture

The app follows a clean architecture with separation of concerns:

| Layer | Components |
|-------|------------|
| **Presentation** | MainActivity, HomeViewModel, Compose UI Components |
| **Domain** | SensitiveDomains, PermissionInspector |
| **Data** | InstalledAppsRepository, PreferencesRepository, NudgeEventRepository |
| **Service** | PrivacyNudgeVpnService, DnsPacketParser, NotificationHelper |

